![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e045896e-3dd8-4320-bd5a-4dce1fc27c0f/Screenshot_20240825_094605.jpg)

*   ## **_Pre Show Results_**
    

Top Flight, Lio Rush, Action Andretti, Tommy Billington, Kyle Fletcher and Kip Sabian defeat Private Party, Dark Order, Anthony Ogogo, Satnam Singh, Ariya Daivari and Jay Lethal via pinfall (pre-show)

Willow Nightingale and Tomohiro Ishii defeat Stokely Hathaway and Kris Statlander via pinfall (pre-show)

Dustin Rhodes, Sammy Guevara, Katsuyori Shibata and the Von Erichs defeat The Kingdom and Cage of Agony (pre-show)

Jamie Hayter returns at All In 2024

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/52969676-4da3-4bed-ac74-9704c64bd7fc/20240825_101503.jpg)

*   ## **_TRIOS CHAMPIONSHIP 4 WAY LADDER MATCH: PAC AND BCC DEF. THE PATRIARCHY (c) VS BANG BANG GANG, AND HOUSE OF BLACK_**
    

PAC finally gets his Wembley moment!!!! Excellent opener that saw Nick Wayne as the MVP.

Post match, House of Black shows respect to PAC.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/84e91f19-8573-45b0-85b5-19527a1d2c8e/20240825_104227.jpg)

## **_AEW WOMEN'S WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: MARIAH MAY DEF. TONI STORM(c)_**

INCREDIBLE match. So violent and stiff. Both women worked hard. Told an excellent story to cap off this top notch storyline.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8713ad86-76da-43b5-ad09-9f527c6ba44a/FB_IMG_1724608120763.jpg)

