TAZ AND HOOK FINALLY SHARE A MOMENT AT WEMBLEY STADIUM

*   ## **_FTW WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP: HOOK DEF. CHRIS JERICHO_**
    

Anything goes match that saw Hook basically win a 3 on 1 Handicap match until Taz got involved and choked out Bryan Keith with the TAZMISSION

